/automatic-garage-doors-its-benefits_default_12_1704445218.png','Automatic garage doors','0',NULL,1,NULL,'2024-01-05 18:32:28','2024-01-06 00:21:38'),(13,2,'Rubber Gym Flooring - Pros and Cons',NULL,'<h1>Rubber Gym Flooring - Pros and Cons</h1>\r\n<p>This guide helps you to know how to buy and how to install the best rubber mat for your gym. This blog takes an in-depth look at rubber flooring to find all the benefits and some important considerations.</p>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/rubber-gym-flooring-pros-and-cons.jpg\" width=\"853\" height=\"448\"></p>\r\n<p>Discover the top rubber flooring pros and cons to help you make a smart shopping decision.</p>\r\n<h2>What is Rubber Gym Flooring?</h2>\r\n<p>Whether you&rsquo;re trying to create a workout room or a commercial gym. Rubber flooring is the ideal surface for your gym, because of its versatility and durability, and low maintenance. There are different types of rubber flooring like interlocking tiles, rolls, mats, and sheets are available as per to fit your space. The material used for rubber flooring is recycled vehicle tires, this makes the flooring extremely strong.</p>\r\n<h2>Rubber flooring has many great advantages:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Durability</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Commercial rubber&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/gymnasiums.php\">gym flooring</a>&nbsp;materials are strong, tough, and long-lasting. Also, these rubber surfaces are hard to gouge, scuff, or scratch. So rubber flooring materials will look good and perform great for many years.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Resistance to heavy impact loads</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Due to the resistance and high density, rubber flooring can withstand thousands of pounds of gym equipment, as well as high impact activity, without rips or tears.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Slip Resistance</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Rubber flooring resists the chance of slipping when it gets wet. That means by installing rubber flooring you have a safe, slip-free surface to work out. And also don&rsquo;t worry about slips causing potential injury.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Water-Resistant</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Installing rubber flooring materials has 100% guaranteed that no water ever reaches your subfloor. You can also seal the flooring with a rubber floor finish and also seal the seams with a seam sealer. Without a finish and sealer, there will be a chance that water can get under the flooring.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Sound absorbance</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Rubber has the ability to absorb sound and muffle the noise, so it is an ideal flooring option for high-traffic areas and cavernous spaces like gyms flooring, stadium floorings where sound bounces off the walls.</p>\r\n<h2>Some important benefits of Gym Flooring are;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Injury prevention</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Versatile</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Durable</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Noise Reduction</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Water resistance and chemical resistance</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Sturdiness</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Impact-absorption</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Resistance to break from falling/dropped weights</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Sensible traction</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Stability</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Luxury look</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>The main drawbacks of rubber gym flooring are;</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Smell</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Rubber flooring material has a distinct smell. This is because of gassing from the glue that holds the flooring and the rubber.</p>\r\n<p>Depending on the type of raw material used or how the flooring was made, some products have strong smells other than others. During the time of installation, the smell will be the strongest. And, a few weeks after installation, the smell will reduce slowly.</p>\r\n<p>Also, you can mop a few times with a mild soap and water cleaning solution and then keep the room well-ventilated or leave the flooring outside to dry. This should alleviate the smell.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Low temperature insulation</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>For temperature transmission rubber is a bad insulator.</p>\r\n<blockquote>Go through the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/blog/outdoor-sports-flooring-factors-to-be-considered.php\">factors to be considered on the installation of outdoor sports flooring</a></blockquote>\r\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\r\n<p>Now that you know the biggest rubber flooring pros and cons.</p>\r\n<p>If you want to upgrade your gym or workout space with the best flooring solution in UAE, get started with some free samples to find the perfect options for you.</p>\r\n<p>For more details, drop us a mail -&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sales@rhinofloor.ae\">sales@rhinofloor.ae</a></p>','Rubber Gym Flooring - Pros and Cons','Is rubber flooring is good for your gym? Why rubber is a favored flooring choice for gyms, lets take a look at the pros and cons of rubber flooring products.','gym flooring, gym flooring in UAE, gym floor, gym floor in uae, gym floor in dubai','rubber-gym-flooring-pros-and-cons','blogs/rubber-gym-flooring-pros-and-cons_default_13_1704445095.jpg','Rubber gym flooring','0',NULL,1,NULL,'2024-01-05 18:33:30','2024-02-28 17:42:03'),(14,2,'5 Important factors to be considered in choosing office flooring',NULL,'<h1>5 Important factors to be considered in choosing office flooring</h1>\r\n<p>Your office interior plays a significant role in identifying the nature of your work and your ability to deal. Every space in the office should have a different type of flooring depending on the nature of work in that area. The entrance should be stunning as always so that it attracts the customer and perfectly represents the brand. The office room floor must be luxurious and trendy, so the client must know that you are aware of current market trends.&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/business-area.php\">Vinyl flooring</a>&nbsp;can be the 