ith a Click System</a></blockquote>\r\n<h2>3. To Prevent Slip-And-Fall Accidents</h2>\r\n<p>One compelling reason why you should install entrance floor mats in your office is to ensure floor safety. Entrance floor mats provide traction to any person who walks from outdoors into your house. If the outdoor weather conditions are wet, then the entrance floor mat will prevent the visitor from slipping and falling as he enters your office.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Bacteria Control</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/entrance-floor-mat.php\">Entrance floor mats</a>&nbsp;treated with an anti-microbial agent can prevent contaminants from entering the environment. This uniqueness would serve to set a home apart from all the rest as well as give it a more appealing tone.</p>\r\n<h2>5. Prevent floor damage</h2>\r\n<p>With well-placed entrance floor mats, you can also prevent damage to the interior floor. It&rsquo;s not just the people that you protect from accidents but also your property.</p>\r\n<blockquote>For more details regarding floor mats, check&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/top-10-essential-types-of-floor-mats-for-your-business-needs.php\">Top 10 Essential Types of Floor Mats For Your Business Needs</a></blockquote>\r\n<h2>Conclusion</h2>\r\n<p>A safe environment is a happy environment. The door mat is a true piece of equipment with a wide variety of functions. Get a front door mat and keep your business safe for all. The safety of employees and clients are of maximum importance to a business owner.</p>\r\n<p>For more details, drop us a mail -&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sales@rhinofloor.ae\">sales@rhinofloor.ae</a></p>','Top 5 tips on the importance of doormats for your office','Read and evaluate the top 5 tips on the importance of doormats for your office.','entrancefloormatsinUAE, entrancefloormats, floormats, floormatsinUAE','why-are-doormats-important-for-your-office','blogs/why-are-doormats-important-for-your-office_default_1704689179.png','doormats',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2024-01-08 17:16:20','2024-01-08 17:16:20'),(29,2,'Top 10 Essential Types of Floor Mats For Your Business Needs',NULL,'<h1>Top 10 Essential Types of Floor Mats For Your Business Needs</h1>\r\n<p>Choosing the right floor mat for your business can increase safety, improve productivity, and even reduce maintenance costs. Rhino Floor provides the best&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/\">floor mats</a>. Use our floor mat guide to make the right choice of floor mats for your business. There is a lot to choose from. Let&rsquo;s see the list of floor mats.</p>\r\n<blockquote>Get a brief at,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/building-a-small-office-space.php\">Building a small office space? Start with the floor!</a></blockquote>\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/essential-types-of-floor-mats.png\" width=\"816\" height=\"428\"></p>\r\n<h2>1. Anti-fatigue Mats</h2>\r\n<p>These are a unique type of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/pvc-floor-tiles.php\">PVC floor mat</a>&nbsp;that features a layered design and enables controlled compression during use. The muscles of the feet, legs, and lower back get stimulated as the mats compress. Also known as ergonomic mats, they keep personnel engaged and alert during long working hours.</p>\r\n<h2>2. Entrance Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Entrance mats are placed at the main entrance of the building. Rhino floor introduces Basmat a leading Spanish manufacturer of entrance matting systems, to provide the best&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/entrance-floor-mat.php\">Entrance floor mats</a>. This entrance mat is composed of aluminum profiles with a carpet, brushes, or rubber insert. The combined action of the different materials acts as a dirt barrier, hence preserving the cleanliness of the buildings&rsquo; floor.</p>\r\n<blockquote>To know more, check&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/tips-to-choose-the-perfect-entrance-mat.php\">Tips to Choose the Perfect Entrance Mat</a></blockquote>\r\n<h2>3. Anti-static Mats</h2>\r\n<p>These are specially designed to reduce the risk of static discharge and electrical shock. These mats are designed for many different environments to increase worker productivity, protect from health risks, and provide a low-maintenance and durable floor covering.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Workstation Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Miltex introduces&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/industrial-floor-mat.php\">industrial floor mats</a>, which can be used in a variety of industries and applications. Workstation mats keep employees fresh and focused. Workstation matting is a cost-effective safety investment capable of delivering consistent dividends to the future. Examples of workstation mats include flooring for the production area, gyms, dairy flooring, warehouse flooring, industrial anti-fatigue flooring, and building entrances.</p>\r\n<blockquote>For more details, check&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/warehouse-and-workshop-floor-long-service-life.php\">Warehouse and Workshop Floors with Long Service Life</a></blockquote>\r\n<h2>5. Indoor Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Interior mats are made specifically for the indoors. They often come in various colors and designs, since there is no need to worry about fading from the sun or damage from other elements. Most indoor mats can remove dirt and water from visitors&rsquo; shoes at the same time look nice in your space.</p>\r\n<h2>6. Wet Area Floor Mats</h2>\r\n<p>In areas exposed to moisture, you\'ll want a mat with good water-resistance and/or drainage holes. The mats should drain away moisture from the surface and enable the subflooring to breathe and dry. These should be soft under bare feet, convenient around a swimming pool area, on a balcony, or in a garage. Rhino floor introduces&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/outdoor-floor-mats.php\">outdoor floor mats</a>&nbsp;that are a popular pattern with high-quality flooring made in Sweden. It is made out of 100% recycled polypropylene material.</p>\r\n<h2>7. Drainage Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Drainage Mats typically feature either holes or slots through which liquids can easily pass, hence making workers safe in environments where liquid spills occur frequently. These mats quickly channel water toward the floor, keeping the walking surface dry and safe.</p>\r\n<h2>8. Logo Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Logo mats are specially designed floor mats that are used for promotional purposes. These mats usually include the logo or brand name of a company to promote brand awareness. You can install them in any strategic place where customers will be able to see them instantly so that the brand name or log becomes imprinted in their minds.</p>\r\n<h2>9. Carpet Mats</h2>\r\n<p>Mostly used in warehouses and industrial locations. They are designed to prevent grime, dust, and dirt from being tracked from outside to indoors, or from a warehouse to an office area. The mats are dense, non-staining, won&rsquo;t crush and are made to last a very long time.</p>\r\n<h2>10. Indoor &amp; Outdoor Mats</h2>\r\n<p>As the name implies, these mats can be placed on the inside or the outside. If a mat is both for indoors and outdoors absorption capability is a must.</p>\r\n<blockquote>For the best flooring for your new business space,&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/why-are-doormats-important-for-your-office.php\">Why are doormats important for your office?</a></blockquote>\r\n<p>Price, quality, and durability are the main criteria to consider in choosing the right floor. Since Rhino Floor mats excel in all these areas, this is the right time to think about it for your floor. Feel free to choose the best mats from the above mentioned list.</p>\r\n<p>For more details, drop us a mail -&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sales@rhinofloor.ae\">sales@rhinofloor.ae</a></p>','Top 10 Essential Types of Floor Mats For Your Business Needs','Get information on the top 10 essential types of floor mats for your business needs.','floor mat, floor tiles, pvc floor tiles, vinyl flooring, indoor floor mat, entrance floor mat, aluminum entrance mat, outdoor floor mat, industrial floor mat','top-10-essential-types-of-floor-mats-for-your-business-needs','blogs/top-10-essential-types-of-floor-mats-for-your-business-needs_default_1704689345.png','Floor Mats',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2024-01-08 17:19:05','2024-01-08 17:19:05'),(30,2,'Where do Rhino Floor Tiles excel in Industrial use?',NULL,'<h1>Where does Rhino Floor Tiles excel in Industrial use?</h1>\r\n<figure><img src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/blog1-1.png\" width=\"669\" height=\"376\"></figure>\r\n<p>Whether your goal is to renovate or overhaul your damaged factory or build entirely new industrial halls, it&rsquo;s best to start with the floor.</p>\r\n<p>In major companies, the choice of the floor usually falls on designers and architects, whereas for smaller buildings the owner alone chooses everything. Whether you belong to the first group or the other, you are probably here to learn more about the applications of&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/\">Floor tiles</a>&nbsp;from Rhino floor. If it&rsquo;s not enough to simply tell you that it makes a good industrial floor, then read on, we will explain what type of floor goes well in industry.</p>\r\n<p>To begin with, it doesn&rsquo;t matter whether PVC floor tiles are better suited as industrial flooring in engineering or production or as flooring in warehouses. Justification can be found anywhere.</p>\r\n<h2>Interlocking tiles on any concrete floor</h2>\r\n<p>Let&rsquo;s have a brief look, for example, the possibilities of renovating concrete floors. There are a lot of them. Cement screeds are good for covering or repairing cracks and leveling the floor. Epoxy coatings are also often used. Another possible choice is&nbsp;<strong>Rhino Floor PVC tiles</strong>. They can be used on polished concrete slabs or a concrete floor of any quality and a more thorough preparation of the substrate is unnecessary. In the case of greater unevenness, however, it is recommended to level out the concrete foundation.</p>\r\n<h2>Properties good for industry</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/commercial-buildings.php\">PVC durable floor tiles</a>&nbsp;can withstand all the pitfalls that await them in industrial plants. Its polymer structure is&nbsp;<strong>resistant to oils and acids</strong>. Water is not a problem, because the locks are tight, and so only a minimum can get underneath them.This minimum, moreover, quickly evaporates through a system of Air Flow channels.Thanks to the non-slip tread, that makes the floor non slippery (for either people or machines). It also belongs to the category of floor coverings with greater fire resistance. It can also take the weight of a forklift truck.</p>\r\n<figure><img class=\"space\" src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/blog1.png\" width=\"829\" height=\"466\"></figure>\r\n<h2>Floor markings</h2>\r\n<p>In manufacturing plants, it is practical to color - distinguish working zones, aisles, forklift corridors, etc. This is usually done by using paint to make stripes and outline individual areas, but colored&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/fortelock.php\">PVC floor tiles</a>&nbsp;take care of this by themselves. Rhino floor has interlocking tiles available in various colors that can be freely combined to create these patterns. In many cases, the floor can be made in the company&rsquo;s colors, as the shades to choose from are really quite a lot. Unlike colored stripes, which gradually peel off, the color of the tiles always stay.</p>\r\n<h2>Fast installation and by yourself</h2>\r\n<p>Price also plays a big role in choosing the right floor. For big manufacturing halls and warehouses, the differences between individual types of floor can range from a few thousand to ten thousands. What could be interesting is that installing industrial PVC floor tiles can mean big savings. As mentioned already, it can be used on any concrete base, and mostly&nbsp;<strong>without glue</strong>. The tiles are simply placed together and hold well with their firm locks. One person can lay&nbsp;<strong>30 m^2</strong>&nbsp;of these PVC interlocking tiles&nbsp;<strong>within one hour</strong>.</p>\r\n<blockquote>To know more, check&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/blog/better-to-choose-a-rubber-or-PVC-floor.php\">Better to choose a rubber or PVC floor?</a></blockquote>\r\n<figure><img class=\"space\" src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/blog1-2.png\" width=\"712\" height=\"401\"></figure>\r\n<h2>Cheap to replace if damaged</h2>\r\n<p>Even if the floor is the best, a sharp object dropped on it can cause damages. In this case Rhino Floor provides the best&nbsp;<a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/heavy-duty-tiles.php\">heavy duty tiles</a>&nbsp;in UAE. The tiles can be changed individually, and so the repair costs are absolute minimum.</p>\r\n<p>Price, quality, durability, and experience with the material are the main criteria to consider in choosing the right floor. Since PVC floor tiles excel in all these areas, this is the right time to think about it for your industrial flooring.</p>\r\n<p>For more details, drop us a mail -&nbsp;<a href=\"mailto:sales@rhinofloor.ae\">sales@rhinofloor.ae</a></p>','Read and evaluate the uses of Rhino Floor pvc tiles for industries.','Read and evaluate the uses of Rhino Floor pvc tiles for industries.','floor tiles, pvc floor tiles, outdoor floor tiles, warehouse flooring, hospital flooring, storage house flooring, event flooring, industrial floor tiles, heavy duty tiles','where-do-rhino-floor-tiles-excel-in-industrial-use','blogs/where-do-rhino-floor-tiles-excel-in-industrial-use_default_1704689788.png','UAE floor tiles','0',NULL,1,NULL,'2024-01-08 17:26:29','2024-01-08 18:18:19'),(31,2,'Tips to Choose The Perfect Entrance Mat',NULL,'<h1>Tips to Choose The Perfect Entrance Mat</h1>\r\n<p>Your entrance mat is one of the first things guests see. Why not spend time creating one that reflects you?</p>\r\n<p>Entrance of your building tells certain stories to