es, or other heavy things. If you or one of the visitors manage to damage your mobile floor, the solution is simple &ndash; instead of replacing the entire floor, just replace the damaged piece.</p>\r\n<h2>Durable interlocks</h2>\r\n<p>The joints between each piece should also be durable. The floor will often be laid and dismounted. Specially designed locks do not change their shape and form a. Since you connect them with a rubber hammer, you do not have to worry about them being damaged. You can use the floor for years, easily adjust the size of the stand, and if any damage happens, replace it with a new one.</p>\r\n<figure><img class=\"space\" src=\"https://www.rhinofloor.ae/images/blog7-5.png\" alt=\"tiles for exhibition floor\"></figure>\r\n<h2>Anti-skid</h2>\r\n<p>Last but not least, take care of security irrespective of where the floor will be located. Whether you want to use it at an exhibition, a birthday party or anywhere else, unless no one will slip on it, you can be less concerned.&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"http://rhinofloor.ae/\">Floor tiles</a>&nbsp;from Rhino Floor comes with anti-skid properties,</strong>&nbsp;which are suitable in areas with high skid and prevent possible accidents.</p>\r\n<h2>Mobile Floor-further use</h2>\r\n<p>The number of situations where it would be good to have a piece of floor with you is pretty big and in some moments, a solid foundation under your feet would bring you more comfort. The advantage of the mobile floor is that you can use it not only for your business but also for your personal needs. In addition to common uses, such as a garage or workshop floor, Rhino products can also be used as a floor for&nbsp;<strong>various social events.</strong></p>\r\n<p>When organizing various celebrations under large tents, the mobile floor can be a&nbsp;<strong>great temporary accessory.</strong>. Thanks to portable flooring systems that will be able to transform almost any space and adjust the atmosphere of your events.</p>\r\n<p>For