rk will be:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>More Efficient</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>More Reliable</strong></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><strong>More DurableEnvironmentally FriendlyHassle-freeNo health risks for your employees</strong></p>\r\n<p>Block cutting machines are an everyday essential for the construction industry. It is used for cutting concrete, paving slabs, natural stone and other masonry in a precise and safe manner. Numerous types of block cutters are available now. But the block cutter from ALMI is different from all the other types.</p>\r\n<blockquote>Read how&nbsp;<a href=\"http://yesautomation.ae/blog/why-industrial-automation-is-important.php\">Industrial Automation is Important</a>&nbsp;in this era</blockquote>\r\n<p>The block splitters from ALMI are welded on a robotic welding cell and the condition for robotic welding is that the parts to be welded are supplied in perfect condition. This results in a high-quality block cutting product.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re looking for a quality&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/block-cutters.php\">block cutter rental in UAE</a>, then contact&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/\">YES Automation</a>. The best metal fabrication rental company that supplies the best quality machinery equipment all around the globe.</p>','Searching for the advantages of ALMI Block Splitters or ALMI Block cutters?','Searching for the advantages of ALMI Block Splitters or ALMI Block cutters?',NULL,'advantages-of-almi-block-splitters','blogs/advantages-of-almi-block-splitters_default_1708602289.jpg','block cutter',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2024-02-23 00:14:49','2024-02-23 00:14:49'),(70,3,'Capacitor-Discharge Welding & its Importance',NULL,'<p>Have you ever thought about the Capacitor-Discharge Welding or CD welding system?</p>\r\n<p>Here, we will be discussing some helpful tips about that, such as Capacitor-Discharge Welding or CD Welding Tips.</p>\r\n<h2>What is a Capacitor-Discharge Welding system?</h2>\r\n<p>A Capacitor-Discharge Welding or CD Welding is the fastest form of resistance welding &amp; utilizes capacitors to deliver power. In this welding system the capacitors are charged with a large amount of energy, and then this charged energy is rapidly released into the parts within milliseconds.</p>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/\">YES Automation</a>&nbsp;offer&rsquo;s CD stud welding machines with high strength, speed, and reliability from a simple process and welding system.</p>\r\n<p>For a closer look at the steps in the capacitor discharge stud welding machine, the welding process occurs in 4 steps.</p>\r\n<p>They are;</p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li><strong>Contact</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Ignition</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Placement (or &lsquo;closing the Gap&rsquo;)</strong></li>\r\n<li><strong>Completion of the Weld Bond</strong></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>At first, the Stud Gun allows &lsquo;contact&rsquo; with the material.</p>\r\n<p>Then the CD gun is triggered passing the weld charge through the Gun, giving ignition of the stud at the stud tip.</p>\r\n<p>At the third step, the &ldquo;tip&rdquo; melts, a small area of the material under the head of the fastener also starts to melt. The Capacitor Discharge gun forces the stud into the melted material, closing the gap between fastener and material, and &ldquo;landing&rdquo; the fastener properly.</p>\r\n<p>In the last step, the stud is held in place as it instantly bonds together with the base material.</p>\r\n<blockquote>Checkout the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/blog/stud-welding-basics-&amp;-benefits.php\">basics and benefits of Stud Welding</a></blockquote>\r\n<h3>Applications</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Projection Welding</li>\r\n<li>Weld nuts and fasteners</li>\r\n<li>Advanced high strength steels</li>\r\n<li>Coated steels</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Advantages</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Uniform high Welding Quality</li>\r\n<li>Requires no re-working on the other side of the weld</li>\r\n<li>Requires no additional material such as flux, inert gas</li>\r\n<li>Elimination Operations like drilling, riveting, etc</li>\r\n<li>No leakages even when welding on containers</li>\r\n<li>No air and water required</li>\r\n<li>The machine can be run on a generator</li>\r\n<li>Voltage fluctuation never effect</li>\r\n<li>No blackish mark on the welded part</li>\r\n<li>Cost of electrodeless</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Features</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Weld counter</li>\r\n<li>Fabricated frame structure for housing the capacitor bank, control circuits, and Welding Transformer</li>\r\n<li>Conservative design and use of proven factors like the electrolytic capacitor, solid- state switches insure long welding life and ease of operation</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Capacitor Discharge Welding Machines that are suitable to join small-diameter studs to thin base metals. 2-3 milliseconds are needed to complete a Capacitor-Discharge Stud welding cycle as thin as 0.02 inches. The short-time welding minimizes the amount of heat generated &amp; penetration depth into the parent material making it ideal for welding smaller diameter ferrous non-ferrous studs on thin gauge base metals.</p>\r\n<p>The stud or fastener can be welded on the reverse side of the coated or finished sheet with very little or no discoloration, distortion, or burning. Stud welding provides a high-quality joint that is strong and resists loosening or breaking.</p>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re looking for quality&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/stud-welders.php\">capacitor discharge welding machines for rental</a>, then contact YES Automation. The best metal fabrication rental company that supplies machinery equipment all around the globe.</p>','Check out the importance of Capacitor Discharge Welding - Yes Automation','Want to know about the basics of Capacitor Discharge Welding and its benefits?',NULL,'capacitor-discharge-welding-its-importance','blogs/capacitor-discharge-welding-its-importance_default_1708602394.jpg','Capacitor-Discharge Welding machines for rents',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2024-02-23 00:16:34','2024-02-23 00:16:34'),(71,3,'Welding Rotators: Basics & Benefits',NULL,'<p>As we all know that, today the welding rotator plays an important role in the welding process. A welding rotator is a type of equipment you can use to make your welding processes easier. Welding Rotators are used to rotate and manipulate Tanks, Pipes, and any other type of cylindrical object. These &ldquo;Welding Rotator/Welding Rollers&rdquo; units provide a wide array of component manipulation and precise rotation speed adjustments as needed for any Tank or Pipe Rotation purposes. This reduces the preparation time and allows the operator to manipulate workpieces to the optimal position.</p>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p>Read on the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/blog/stud-welding-basics-&amp;-benefits.php\">basics and benefits of Stud Welding machine</a></p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p><strong>Types of Tank Rotators&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Conventional Tank Rotators</li>\r\n<li>Self-aligned Tank Rotators</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Conventional Tank Rotators</h2>\r\n<p>Conventional Welding Rotators are a type of welding rotator manufactured by using optimum quality steel material and cutting-edge technology. To ensure its operational safety and performance, the rotator machines are strictly checked on various quality parameters under the supervision of quality testing engineers. Offered Conventional Tank Rotator is highly acclaimed for the below-mentioned characteristics:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Easy &amp; safe operations</li>\r\n<li>Prolonged working life</li>\r\n<li>Resistance against corrosion &amp; abrasion</li>\r\n<li>Ultraviolet stability</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>Self-aligned Tank Rotators</h2>\r\n<p>Self-aligning tank rotator feature of the wheel brackets allows the wheels to automatically align themselves when a pipe or vessel is loaded onto the sections, irrespective of ovality, to accommodate any diameter within their range.</p>\r\n<p>With a conventional rotator, the wheel brackets have to be adjusted manually across the frames to accommodate the varying diameters within their range.</p>\r\n<h3>Bode Patented Self-Aligning Rotators</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Instantly self-aligning to the workpiece.</li>\r\n<li>Robust all-steel welded construction.</li>\r\n<li>Clutches are incorporated in top rollers of the Drive Section to prevent damage to the transmission when loading.</li>\r\n<li>Variable speed rotation through AC inverter control.</li>\r\n<li>Tachometer speed indicator (optional).</li>\r\n<li>Anti-Creep fitted to ldler Section (optional).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>As is to be expected of Bode machinery, all Traversing Self-Aligning Rotators are built to the highest standards with quality materials and components:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Robust, all-steel construction</li>\r\n<li>Inverter-controlled traversing and rotation at welding speeds.</li>\r\n<li>All rollers of the Drive Section are positively driven.</li>\r\n<li>Clutches are incorporated in top rollers of the Drive Section to prevent damage to transmission during loading.</li>\r\n<li>On unloading easy-pivot roller brackets operate in reverse, moving to their resting position, ready to take the next piece.</li>\r\n<li>Idler Section can incorporate a manual or electric anti-creep feature to restrict vessel &lsquo;creep&rsquo; to +/&ndash; 1 mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Welding Rotator Applications</h3>\r\n<p>Most common applications you can have of it include the welding of:</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Storage Tanks</li>\r\n<li>Water Tanks</li>\r\n<li>Shipyards and Ship Components</li>\r\n<li>Pressure Vessels</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Benefits and Advantages of Welding Rotators</h3>\r\n<p>The benefits and advantages of using welding rotators are endless. Some of the most common benefits and advantages are;</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Increased Productivity</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>One of the primary benefits of using welding rotators is that you get increased productivity. It is because you wouldn&rsquo;t be meddling with the workpiece, your welders can stay in one position and perform the weld. This can actually be efficient and effective in promoting your overall productivity.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Safe</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>With a welding rotator, the workers don&rsquo;t need to worry or think about manually handling workpieces; you can mount them onto the welding rotator so they&rsquo;ll move, rotate, and spin automatically.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Quality Welds</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>By automating the rotation of the workpieces, you can be sure that the high-quality welds, accurate, and more precise.100% match the plan and the results you are expecting to get.</p>\r\n<h3>Disadvantages of Using Welding Rotator</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Only Effective in Materials With Good Weldability</li>\r\n<li>Required experience</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<blockquote>Learn the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/blog/kistler-programmable-pipe-cutting-machines-review.php\">complete review of Kistler Programmable pipe cutting machine</a></blockquote>\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re looking for a quality&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/welding-rotators.php\">Tank or Pipe Welding Rotators rental in UAE</a>, then contact&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.yesautomation.ae/\"><strong>YES Automation</strong></a>. The best metal fabrication rental company that supplies machinery equipment all around the globe.</p>','Basics & Benefits of High-Quality Welding Rotators','Want to know about the basics and benefits of Welding Rotators? Visit the given blog here to learn more about all the useful information about Welding Rotators.',NULL,'welding-rotators-basics-benefits','blogs/welding-rotators-basics-benefits_default_1708602502.jpg','welding rotators',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,'2024-02-23 00:18:22','2024-02-23 00:18:22'),(72,3,'We are also part of Dubai Expo 2020 - Yes Automation',NULL,'<p>World Expo 2020 is currently hosted by Dubai in the United Arab Emirates (UAE) from 1st October 2021 to 31st Marc